overview.en: ATCLUB NETWORK TECHNOLOGY LLC is the first e-commerce + social + small video + public chain + project complex in the world. It aims to use block chain to lock consumer groups with the mode of blasting powder, and use tip mechanism to lock the fans of merchants at different levels to improve consumer loyalty.
overview.zh: ATCLUB NETWORK TECHNOLOGY LLC是全球首个电商+社交+小视频+公链+项目方综合体，旨在用区块链的方式，利用爆粉模式锁定消费人群，利用打赏机制将商家的粉丝层层锁定，提高消费用户粘性。
